      "content": "it just feels so selfish to keep clinging to this life when i know i'm just making things harder for everyone else. like, if i wasn't here, the cycle of stress and misery would just stop. i'm just thinking about how much more they could achieve if they didn't have to spend all their energy worrying about me.",
